On Escalation Ticket # 00435643 the new comment has been added: Oana-Cristina Rus:

Hi,



What I noticed from the attached log is that the last three patches were added as offline patches. The previous online patch applied with success was on 2024.02.01.

After this date, all the update patches logs return the same error message 'Update Archive checksum does not match the received checksum from Live Update Server'.

1. You can try to apply the offline patch for 5941.


2. The customer needs to check why the live update download doesn't work.

telnet liveupdate.endpointprotector.com was connecting but then immediately closing. 

Can you please check if the firewall is blocking HTTP traffic? Verify if outbound/inbound rules are blocking port 80 (HTTP) and 443 (HTTPS). It is possible that after port 80 was whitelisted, the online patch started downloading.

@WaitingOnDevOps
